{"tid":1065202,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★外星科技】調查指逾6成文憑試聆聽試考生　沒用過收音機","createTime":"2019-03-17T05:58:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T15:29:55.000Z","uid":19454,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"3e43c381d0cbde70e11307d1e878ef6cf56b5845","tid":1065202,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T05:58:08.000Z","msg":"有團體的調查發現，超過6成受訪應屆文憑試考生，沒有使用過具收聽電台廣播功能的耳筒式收音機。有應屆考生說，不熟悉收音機用法，擔心影響考試表現。<br />\n<br />\n團體青年新世界建議，考評局檢討聆聽考試模式，考慮改用紅外線接收系統廣播。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1448115-20190317.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1448115-20190317.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=vfAPSPM9tzlrjOAF5hGH%2Fwmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=70bd1fd8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1448115-20190317.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=3134665c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1448115-20190317.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"328f548855ab72ed9fad96847790c112c73ec7d9","tid":1065202,"uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T05:58:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QFVSZO8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQFVSZO8.png&h=44600e0d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d943942d0dd060a6a8db8d81e7be628b0ce1d478","tid":1065202,"uid":63846,"like":11,"dislike":10,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T05:59:03.000Z","msg":"00後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4c5586363e895fc57787d1baf40e0a5663d35a5","tid":1065202,"uid":91722,"like":38,"dislike":8,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T05:59:22.000Z","msg":"垃撚圾00後"},{"pid":"4513fddead20525d5d5fccedfec74f39f777b179","tid":1065202,"uid":19454,"like":61,"dislike":2,"score":59